So I FINALLY get 10 people into a channel, petition a GM and then we have to go into a chat...... well that was one of the harder parts, I had to explain in great detail how to enter a chat channel at the server select, seeing as no one ever uses it. I finally did it, get everyone in, get everyone to #guildapprove.... So I type #guildmake blah blah blah get to the name part... Type in my old guild's name (WHICH I KNOW NO OTHER GUILD OWNS THIS NAME, THIS GUILD WAS JUST DELETED 2 months ago!) and it says its not a unique name? Wtf? Okay so I go back into the channel, ask the people for a new name.... get several answers, so I go try them all.... Finally one works &quot;Endless Evolution&quot; sad name I know... Okay, we all go back in game, I talk to a GM again and says I have to wait anywhere from 5days, weeks, or months..... WTF? For christs sakes all they have to do is review the name, tag it as okay, send a small pre-made email, and then an in-game GM adds you..... how the @#%* hard is that!?<br>
<br>
